    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Re-description and systematic re-appraisal of the genus Kokkocynips Pujade-Villar & Melika, (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini), including new combinations of Nearctic species and the description of a new species from Panama" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563820>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563826>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563828>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563822>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563832>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563834>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563838>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563840>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563842>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563844> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563820>
    dc:description "FIG. 1. Majority-rule consensus tree of species sampled from across the Cynipini, based on a Bayesian analysis of a concatenation of three loci (cytochrome b, long-wavelength opsin, and the D2 region of the 28S rRNA gene). Black stars at nodes indicate ±95% posterior probability support; white stars indicate 70%-94% posterior probability support. The revised limits of the genus Kokkocynips are indicated by the grey shaded box." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563826>
    dc:description "FIG. 3. Kokkocynips panamensis, new species, asexual female. (A) Pronotum, antero-dorsal view. (B) Mesosoma, dorsal view. (C) Mesosoma, lateral view. (D) Hind leg. (E) Metasoma, lateral view. (F) Metatarsal claw. (G) Detail of the ventral spine of the hypopygium, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563826/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563828>
    dc:description "FIG. 4. Kokkocynips panamensis, new species, asexual female. (A) Forewing. (B) Habitus. (C) Section of gall showing the alive cynipid. (D) Section of a mature galls on Quercus salicifolia. (E) External view of a gall." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563828/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563822>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. Kokkocynips panamensis, new species, asexual female. (A) Head, anterior view. (B) Head, posterior view. (C) Head, dorsal view. (D) Propodeum. (E) Female antenna. (F) Detail of the last flagellomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563822/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563832>
    dc:description "FIG. 5. Kokkocynips doctorrosae Pujade-Villar from Oaxaca (México), female, SEM pictures. (A) Head anterior view. (B) Mesosoma dorsal view. (C) Mesosoma lateral view (D) Propodeum posterior view. (E) Antenna. (F) Metasoma lateral view. (G) Detail of sculpture on terga." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563832/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563834>
    dc:description "FIG. 6. Kokkocynips imbricariae (Ashmead), n. comb., female, SEM pictures. (A) Head anterior view. (B) Head posterior view. (C) Mesoscutellum (D) Mesosoma lateral view. (E) Metasoma lateral view. (F) Mesoscutum dorso-lateral view. (G) Metatarsal claw. (H) Antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563834/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563838>
    dc:description "FIG. 7. Kokkocynips coxii (Bassett), n. comb., female, SEM pictures. (A) Head dorsal view. (B) Head anterior view. (C) Mesosoma dorsal view (D) Mesosoma lateral view. (E) Propodeum. (F) Metasoma lateral view. (G) Antenna. (H) Hypopygium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563838/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563840>
    dc:description "FIG. 8. Kokkocynips rileyi (Ashmead), n. comb., female, SEM pictures. (A) Head dorsal view. (B) Head anterior view. (C) Mesosoma dorsal view (D) Mesosoma lateral view. (E) Propodeum. (F) Metasoma lateral view.. (G) Metatarsal claw. (H) Hypopygium" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563840/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563842>
    dc:description "FIG. 9. Kokkocynips difficilis (Ashmead), n. comb., female, SEM pictures. (A) Head dorsal view. (B) Head anterior view. (C) Mesosoma dorsal view (D) Mesosoma lateral view. (E) Propodeum. (F) Metasoma lateral view. (G) Detail of mesoscutellar foveae. (H). Hypopygium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563842/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4563844>
    dc:description "FIG. 10. Female habitus of species of Kokkocynips. (A) Kokkocynips decidua (Beutenmueller) n. comb. (B) Kokkocynips doctorrosae Pujade-Villar. (C) Kokkocynips coxii (Bassett) n. comb. (D) Kokkocynips rileyi (Ashmead) n. comb. (E) Kokkocynips difficilis (Ashmead) n. comb. (F) Kokkocynips imbricariae (Ashmead) n. comb." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4563844/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

